@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Inicio - ForoU";
}

<style>
    .forou-home {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 24px;
    }

    .forou-banner {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6670ff 0%, #8a4fff 55%, #25164b 100%);
        border: 1px solid rgba(123, 137, 255, 0.18);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 34px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

        .forou-banner::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 260px;
            height: 260px;
            right: -70px;
            top: -70px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .forou-banner::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 160px;
            height: 160px;
            right: 120px;
            bottom: -80px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

    .forou-banner-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        max-width: 850px;
    }

    .forou-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 8px 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .forou-banner h1 {
        margin: 0 0 14px 0;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .forou-banner p {
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 760px;
    }

    .forou-banner-actions {
        margin-top: 24px;
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .forou-btn-main {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 13px 20px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        background: #fff;
        color: #151a2f;
    }

        .forou-btn-main:hover {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #151a2f;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

    .forou-btn-alt {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 13px 20px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #fff;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.28);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

        .forou-btn-alt:hover {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
        }

    .forou-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .forou-card {
        background: #111328;
        border: 1px solid rgba(123, 137, 255, 0.12);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
    }

    .forou-card-icon {
        width: 52px;
        height: 52px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: rgba(109,121,255,0.12);
        border: 1px solid rgba(109,121,255,0.22);
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .forou-card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 12px 0;
        font-size: 25px;
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 800;
    }

    .forou-card p {
        margin: 0 0 18px 0;
        color: #c7d0f1;
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        min-height: 96px;
    }

    .forou-card a {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #dbe2ff;
        border: 1px solid rgba(123, 137, 255, 0.26);
    }

        .forou-card a:hover {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
        }

    .forou-panel {
        background: #111328;
        border: 1px solid rgba(123, 137, 255, 0.12);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 28px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
    }

        .forou-panel h2 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #fff;
        }

    .forou-panel-sub {
        color: #c7d0f1;
        font-size: 17px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .forou-list {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 16px;
    }

    .forou-list-item {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
        border: 1px solid rgba(123, 137, 255, 0.10);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 18px;
    }

        .forou-list-item strong {
            display: block;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .forou-list-item span {
            color: #c7d0f1;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

    @@media (max-width: 1100px) {
        .forou-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .forou-list {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .forou-banner h1 {
            font-size: 38px;
        }

        .forou-banner p {
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    }
</style>
    <section class="forou-panel">
        <h2>¿Qué podés hacer en ForoU?</h2>
        <div class="forou-panel-sub">
            Un espacio pensado para la comunicación universitaria de forma clara y ordenada.
        </div>

        <div class="forou-list">
            <div class="forou-list-item">
                <strong>Crear publicaciones</strong>
                <span>Planteá dudas, abrí discusiones académicas y compartí consultas con otras personas.</span>
            </div>

            <div class="forou-list-item">
                <strong>Responder hilos</strong>
                <span>Colaborá en conversaciones activas y aportá respuestas dentro de cada categoría.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</div>